## Project Overview üìã

### Background  
This project provides a comprehensive analysis of retail promotional campaigns during Diwali and Sankranti across South Indian cities. It evaluates the effectiveness of various promotions, sales performance, and revenue generation across store locations, product categories, and promotion types.

### Business Problem  
- Evaluate the effectiveness of campaigns across different dimensions.  
- Understand geographic and category-wise performance variations.  
- Identify optimal promotion types.  
- Analyze the relationship between pricing and sales.

### Scope  
- **Geographic Coverage**: 10 major South Indian cities  
- **Categories**: Grocery & Staples, Home Care, Personal Care, Home Appliances, and Combo products  
- **Promotion Types**: BOGOF (Buy One Get One Free), Cashback, Percentage Discounts  
- **Time Period**: Diwali and Sankranti festival seasons  

